• 1 sliding ballast B of mass 240 g, l0 = 0 m and L = 2.6 m, see Fig. 4(a). • 1 sliding buoy B of mass 130 g and an anchor A of 2 kg, l0 = 2.75 m and L = 3 m, see Fig. 4(b). • 1 fixed ballast M of mass 240 g and 1 siding buoy B of mass 130 g, l0 = 2.2 m and L = 2.2 m, see Fig. 4(c). • 1 sliding ballast B of mass 240 g, l0 = 0 m and L = 3 m, equipped with two IMUs, see Fig. 5.
